org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver

Class AccessPointAuthChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.cdxserver.auth.PrivTokenAuthChecker
      • org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver.AccessPointAuthChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthChecker

    public class AccessPointAuthChecker
extends PrivTokenAuthChecker
    AuthChecker implementation that runs ExclusionFilter provided through AccessPoint.getExclusionFactory() as well as the filtering provided by WaybackAPAuthChecker.

    This is primarily meant for running CustomPolicyOracleFilter in CDXServer rather than in EmbeddedCDXServerIndex, making WaybackAPAuthChecker obsolete. Current implementation is very specific to this usage.

    Needs APContextAuthToken as token.
